630
00:42:30,380 --> 00:42:34,639
Share your experiences when you were distressed and heartbroken.

631
00:42:34,639 --> 00:42:36,900
Encourage her to be positive about life.

632
00:42:38,120 --> 00:42:40,910
What? What's with this expression?

633
00:42:40,910 --> 00:42:43,960
You make me feel like I'm a bottle of poison.

634
00:42:43,960 --> 00:42:46,679
