00:43:13,180 --> 00:43:16,319
It's so dark right now. Be careful.

648
00:43:18,380 --> 00:43:20,460
What are you laughing at?

649
00:43:21,080 --> 00:43:23,489
I'll help you up. I got you.

650
00:43:23,489 --> 00:43:25,920
We're severing all ties for three days!

651
00:43:25,920 --> 00:43:27,740
Don't touch me!

652
00:43:27,740 --> 00:43:30,980
I'm sorry. My bad. Won't an apology do?

653
00:43:30,980 --> 00:43:32,280
- Hongdou!
- Leave me alone.

